{"word":"ὕπαιθᾰ","slug":"ὕπαιθᾰ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n106814\" key=\"u(/paiqă\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ὕπαιθᾰ</orth>, <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adv.\">Adv.</a></pos>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ὑπό, ὑπαί</etym>) <sense id=\"n106814.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">out under, under and away,</tr_> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὕ. λιάσθη</foreign> yielded <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">before</tr_> him, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">under</tr_> his attack, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:15:520\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.520</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ποταμὸς . . ὕ. ῥέων</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:21:271\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.271</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἡ δὲ [πέλεια] ὕ. φοβεῖται</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:22:141\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.141</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κατακέκλιται ἤπειρόνδε κοίλη ὕ. νάπη</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:735\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.R.\">A.R.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.735</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n106814.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> Prep. with gen. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">under,</tr_> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">αἱ μὲν ὕπαιθα ἄνακτος ἐποίπνυον</foreign> (sc. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">αἱ ἀμφίπολοι</foreign>) <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">under</tr_> him, so as to support him, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:18:421\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.421</biblScope> </bibl>; of one shrinking <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">under</tr_> an attack, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὕπαιθα δὲ τοῖο λιασθεὶς φεῦγ᾽</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:21:255\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.255</biblScope></bibl></cit>. (Expld. as <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">εἰς τὸ ἰθὺ καὶ ἀντικρὺ καὶ ἔμπροσθεν</foreign> in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4083.tlg001:1030:20\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eust.\">Eust.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1030.20</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4083.tlg001:1234:11\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1234.11</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4083.tlg001:1262:61\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1262.61</biblScope> </bibl>; as <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐκ πλαγίου</foreign> in Sch.<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.R.\">A.R.</a></author> </bibl> l.c., denied or doubted by <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eust.\">Eust.</a></author> </bibl> ll. cc.)</sense> </entryFree>"}]}